I thought the course was great. The videos were short and straight to the point. The instructor spoke clearly and used simple language. There are tons of files and resources provided as well. A key takeaway for me is the importance of sketching out logo concepts before working in Illustrator. It's a simple idea but once you start doing it you see how quickly you can run through different concepts and choose the best designs to move forward with. You can expect to learn other things such as the different types of logos, how to brainstorm design ideas, what not to do in your logo designs, and much more.

Overall I'd recommend this course to anyone interested in learning logo design.
